attribution.changeMessage: Match in all times and dates and places as far as I can see.  Matches my memory and notes of her passing.  Her name at birth was Lena Temperance Dehaven.  Name at marriage and death Lena Temperance Little.  Grave marker reads Lena DeHaven Little as remembrance of her father William Alexander DeHaven. See his memorial on find a grave. His birth 1847 and death in 1931 occuring in Missouri.

Looks correct by all evidence given including prior zip code in Highland Park area of Los Angeles on Irvington Place.  Age should be 100 unless rounding up is the standard which would make it 101.  Close enough.
Matches all other records available for my grandparents, Mena and Roy, including death certificate for Roy, my maternal grandfather.  I have a certified copy of his death cert.
